<p><a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/refer/kadence-wp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" title="Kadence WP">Kadence WP</a> is a performance-focused theme that gives you premium-level design control, even in the free version. It’s fast, flexible, and great for anyone who wants speed without giving up customization.</p>



<p>While Kadence WP scored a B in my performance tests, I&#8217;ve included it in my top list because its powerful free design features are unmatched. Plus, it can still have great performance with the right setup.</p>



<h5 class="wp-block-heading" id="aioseo-my-experience">My Experience</h5>



<p>One standout feature is the Header and Footer Builder, which lets you create fully <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-themes/how-to-create-a-custom-page-in-wordpress/" title="How to Create a Custom Page in WordPress">custom layouts</a> with simple drag-and-drop. I usually find this feature locked behind paid upgrades in other themes, but Kadence includes it for free.</p>



<p>Kadence also scores points for performance. Many optimizations happen out of the box, so beginners don’t need to mess with settings.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="366" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/kadence-gtmetrix-b.png" alt="Kadence's GTmetrix speed test results" class="wp-image-363397" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/kadence-gtmetrix-b.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/kadence-gtmetrix-b-300x161.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<p>Global <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/how-to-choose-a-perfect-color-scheme-for-your-wordpress-site/" title="How to Choose a Perfect Color Scheme for Your WordPress Site">color palettes</a> and font controls make it easy to keep your branding consistent across your site. When paired with Kadence Blocks, the Gutenberg block editor transforms into a powerful design system.</p>



<p>The theme also includes a starter library of professional templates for different business types or <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/showcase/best-blogging-niche-that-will-make-money-easily/" title="Best Blogging Niche – That Will Make Money (Easily)">blog niches</a>. These can be imported in just a few clicks, giving you a polished starting point that still maintains Kadence’s speed.</p>



<p>🧑‍💻 <strong>Why I recommend Kadence WP:</strong> If you want premium-level customization and fast performance without buying a paid theme, <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/refer/kadence-wp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" title="Kadence WP">Kadence WP</a> is an excellent choice. It’s especially well-suited for designers. </p>



